text:
Julymar Otero (born 31 October 1996, Toa Baja, Puerto Rico) is a female volleyball player. She is a member of the Puerto Rico women's national volleyball team. She was part of the Puerto Rican National Team at the 2013 U18 Youth Pan American Cup, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship.
She played for College of Central Florida, and Towson University.
